SUBI README
  Notes for users and developers on the Subi data entry and retrival system
  Most users will only be interested in the basic installation instructions.
  See the table of contents below.

ABOUT SUBI
  subi is made to make it easy to digitize a radiobiology archive and search
  through the results.  Usage instructions are baked into the application.
  This README shows how to get subi running.

